- In `mopsus`, replace the `dataroom` subprocess in `run_think.py`'s summary fetch with an MCP call when `MOPSUS_SUMMARY_BACKEND=mcp`. Keep CLI path as fallback.
- Files touched: ~1 new file in dataroom, ~1 function in mopsus, 2 config snippets. Reversible by env var.

### Smallest reversible experiment

- **One week, behind a flag.** Implement `dataroom-mcp` exposing only `latest(channel, hours)` — read-only, no writes, no summarise.
